    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "TechArticle",
    "headline": "中国移动云能力中心：基于openEuler的安全可信技术探索和实践",
    "description": "基于openEuler的安全可信技术探索和实践，将可信计算能力与中国商用密码算法体系相结合，实现云主机全方位安全可信保障。",
    "url": "https://www.openeuler.openatom.cn/zh/showcase/cloud-computing/kexinyun",
    "inLanguage": "zh",
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
